+{"id":"bd-mblr.3.2.2","title":"Scenario-to-script coverage drift CI gate","description":"Add CI checker that validates canonical scenario catalog coverage against script/test traceability manifests and fails when required scenarios are unmapped or unexecuted in required lanes. Output: machine-readable gap diff and human summary.","design":"Compare canonical scenario catalog against script/test traceability and executed lane manifests to detect both mapping drift and execution drift.","acceptance_criteria":"1. CI validates canonical scenario catalog coverage against script/test manifests and required execution lanes. 2. Fails when required scenarios are unmapped or not executed with required artifacts/logging. 3. Produces machine-readable gap diff and concise operator summary for remediation.","notes":"This gate consumes consolidated script-suite readiness via bd-mblr.4.5.3 and core matrix behavior via bd-mblr.3.2.1. It is intentionally decoupled from final script-log conformance gate (bd-mblr.5.5.3) so scenario-drift enforcement can be implemented earlier, with combined assurance enforced later at CI policy level.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-13T00:44:32.043386147Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-13T01:32:41.030328633Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.3.2.2","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.3.2","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-13T01:31:20.998504842Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.3.2.2","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.3.2.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-13T00:44:47.633253091Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.3.2.2","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.4.1.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-13T00:44:46.539768818Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.3.2.2","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.4.5.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-