 {"id":"bd-mblr.3.4","title":"No-Mock Critical-Path Enforcement Gate","description":"Add CI assertion that each designated critical path has at least one non-mock, real-backend test lane and that this requirement is reviewed when new critical paths are introduced.","design":"Drive validation from invariant coverage matrix instead of ad-hoc hardcoded test name lists.","acceptance_criteria":"- Gate validates each critical invariant/path has at least one non-mock test lane in required CI execution.
